NAME
     9x more scum & rats than rio. Just say NEIN.

DESCRIPTION
     9x is a scummy X11 window manager. A rat infested rio rip-off.
     It provides far more than you bargained for.
     Do 9 things and do them poorly.

OPTIONS
     -v  Erase computer. Weep.

MOUSE
   Window Tabs
     Button 1    Focus.
     Button 2    Delete.
     Button 3    Re-Sweep.
     Doubleclick Maximize.

   Window Borders
     Button 1         Resize.
     Button 2         Delete.
     Button 3         Move.
     Doubleclick Top  Maximize.
     Doubleclick Side Tile to side.

